No unified reconciliation
Businesses lose track of transactions
What you build:
A unified payment brain inside ERPNext
Advanced features:
Auto-detect incoming payments (via APIs or SMS parsing)
Smart reconciliation:
Match payments to invoices automatically
Multi-provider abstraction layer:
Airtel Money
TNM Mpamba
Banks
Offline USSD-triggered payments
Fraud detection (duplicate / suspicious transactions)
